  "title": "Land Surveyor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Visit www.ppsjob.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Land Surveyor</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Reports to:</strong> Project Engineer</p>\n<p><strong>Duties:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct land and engineering surveys for construction projects, site boundaries, and land titles.</li>\n  <li>Perform setting out of building grid lines before and during construction.</li>\n  <li>Carry out surveys related to land use, housing, and traffic patterns.</li>\n  <li>Conduct routine building alignment surveys throughout the project.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree or Diploma in Land Surveying or related qualification.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years’ experience in building surveying.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of precast installation and verticality control is a plus.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Interested? Apply now to join our surveying team!  Visit www.ppsjob.com.sg</strong></p>",
